P0100.causes:
The Engine is SputteringThere are multiple parts that keep an engine running well but a 
            misfiring or sputtering engine is one of the most common issues. For an engine to run efficiently 
            the right amount of air and fuel must mix and then burn within the combustion chamber. In order for 
            this to run correctly there are a number of components in the fuel and ignition systems that have to 
            work in unison.
